'''Adrienne Ako Anomgbo Koutouan''' (wavutse 1969)  numukinnyi wa filimi na comedi muri  Cote d'Ivoire.

== Ubuzima ==
Koutouan ni umwe mu baturage ba Tchaman kandi yavukiye mu mudugudu wa Abobo-Té muri komine ya Abobo hafi ya Abidjan .  Yifuzaga kuba umukinnyi wa filimi kuva akiri umwana, nubwo iki gitekerezo kitakiriwe neza n'ababyeyi be. Yatangiye umwuga we mu myaka ya za 1980 mu itsinda ry’ikinamico "Fétiche éburnéen".  Mu 1986, Koutouan yagizwe umubyinnyi mwiza muri ballet ya Coryte d'Ivoire. 

Koutouan yahawe ibihembo byinshi, harimo kwitwara neza mu bagore mu iserukiramuco rya Namur mu Bubiligi mu 1998, kwitwara neza mu bagore mu iserukiramuco rya M-Net ryabereye i Johannesburg mu 1999, ndetse n’umukinnyi  wa [[Afurika]] witwaye neza mu iserukiramuco rya Pabbah muri [[Nijeriya]] mu 2002.  Mu mwaka wa 2006, Koutouan yahawe igihembo cya Gold Standard mu iserukiramuco rya Filime na Televiziyo bya Panafrican rya Ouagadougou kubera kwitwara neza mu rukurikirane rwa ''Quand les éléphants se battent'' . Azwi cyane muri Coryte [[Kote Divuwari|d'Ivoire]] kubera uruhare rwe nka Rosalie mu rukurikirane rwa ''Faut pas fâcher'' .  Muri 2008, Koutouan yakinnye nka Infirmière Antoinette muri Dr. Boris ari kumwe na Ahmed Souaney. 

Ku ya 14 Mata 2019, Koutouan yahawe icyubahiro mu birori byo kwizihiza imyaka 30 amaze ari umukinnyi wa filime, ahabwa itandukaniro riturutse kuri guverinoma. Yageze ku ntera ya ofisiye mu cyubahiro cy’umuco, na Minisiteri y’umuco na Francophonie. Umugatolika wubahaga Imana, Koutouan na we yagize misa mu cyubahiro cye. 

